object.script:
pi2 = math.pi*2
function onTick() local here = { input.getNumber(4), input.getNumber(8), input.getNumber(12) } local heading = input.getNumber(16) local yaw = math.fmod(0.75-heading, 1)*pi2 -- compass to radians from east, +ve = clockwise local pitch = input.getNumber(20)*pi2 local roll = input.getNumber(24)*pi2 for i = 0, 7 do local isActive = input.getBool(i+1) if isActive then local dist = input.getNumber(i*4 + 1) local azimuth = input.getNumber(i*4 + 2) * pi2 local elev = input.getNumber(i*4 + 3) * pi2 --local p = { math.cos(azimuth)*dist, -math.sin(azimuth)*dist, math.sin(elev)*dist } local ce = math.cos(elev) local p = { dist*ce*math.cos(azimuth), -dist*ce*math.sin(azimuth), dist*math.sin(elev) } --[[ x = r * cos(polar) * cos(alpha) y = r * cos(polar) * sin(alpha) z = r * sin(polar) where: r is the Radius alpha is the horizontal angle from the X axis polar is the vertical angle made by r vector with the x-y plane ( 90 - <angle with Z axis> ) ]] local cr = math.cos(roll) local sr = math.sin(roll) p = matMulVec(p, { 1, 0, 0, 0, cr, sr, 0, -sr, cr, }) local cp = math.cos(pitch) local sp = math.sin(pitch) p = matMulVec(p, { cp, 0, -sp, 0, 1, 0, sp, 0, cp, }) local cy = math.cos(yaw) local sy = math.sin(yaw) p = matMulVec(p, { cy, sy, 0, -sy, cy, 0, 0, 0, 1, }) p = vadd(p, here) output.setBool(i+1, true) output.setNumber(i*3+1, p[1]) output.setNumber(i*3+2, p[2]) output.setNumber(i*3+3, p[3]) end end end
function distanceSq(a, b) return (a[1]-b[1])^2 + (a[2]-b[2])^2 + (a[3]-b[3])^2 end function vadd(a, b) return {a[1]+b[1],a[2]+b[2],a[3]+b[3]} end function vmul(a, f) return {a[1]*f,a[2]*f,a[3]*f} end
function matMulVec(v, m) return { m[1]*v[1] + m[2]*v[2] + m[3]*v[3], m[4]*v[1] + m[5]*v[2] + m[6]*v[3], m[7]*v[1] + m[8]*v[2] + m[9]*v[3], } end

throttle = 0
function onTick() delta = input.getNumber(1) sensitivity = input.getNumber(2) / 60 -- per second to per tick throttle = math.min(math.max(throttle + delta * sensitivity, 0), 1) output.setNumber(1, throttle) end

object.script:
-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() ap = input.getBool(1) speed = input.getNumber(1) maxSpeed = input.getNumber(2) fuel = input.getNumber(3) fuelMax = input.getNumber(4) fuelMultiplier = input.getNumber(5) battery = input.getNumber(6) rps = input.getNumber(7) maxRps = input.getNumber(8) currentGear = input.getNumber(9) fuelFlow = input.getNumber(10) throttle = input.getNumber(11) sounding = input.getNumber(12) end
radiusSpeedIndicator = 15 radiusRpmIndicator = 10 fuelRateMode = 1 -- 0 = Endurance, 1 = Range, 2 = Rate
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight()
speedIndicatorXOffset = w/2 speedIndicatorYOffset = h -- Speed Dial screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) screen.drawCircle(speedIndicatorXOffset, speedIndicatorYOffset, radiusSpeedIndicator+1) speedKnots = math.abs(speed * 1.94384) speedCalc = 275 + (speedKnots/maxSpeed) * 170 throttleAngle = 275 + throttle * 170
drawTick(speedIndicatorXOffset, speedIndicatorYOffset, speedCalc, 0, radiusSpeedIndicator-0.5) screen.setColor(255, 255, 0) drawTick(speedIndicatorXOffset, speedIndicatorYOffset, throttleAngle, radiusSpeedIndicator+1, 3)
--speed number screen.setColor(255,255,0) screen.drawTextBox(speedIndicatorXOffset-8, speedIndicatorYOffset-6, 16, 4, math.floor(speedKnots), 1, 0)
rpmIndicatorXOffset = w * 6/7 rpmIndicatorYOffset = h -- rps Dial screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) screen.drawCircle(rpmIndicatorXOffset, rpmIndicatorYOffset, radiusRpmIndicator+1) rpm = math.abs(rps) rpmCalc = 270 + (rpm/maxRps) * 180 x2 = rpmIndicatorXOffset + (radiusRpmIndicator -0.5) * math.sin(math.pi * 2 * rpmCalc / 360) y2 = rpmIndicatorYOffset - (radiusRpmIndicator -0.5) * math.cos(math.pi * 2 * rpmCalc / 360) screen.drawLine(rpmIndicatorXOffset, rpmIndicatorYOffset, x2, y2) --rps number screen.setColor(255,0,0) screen.drawTextBox(rpmIndicatorXOffset-5, rpmIndicatorYOffset-6, 10, 4, math.floor(rpm), 0, 0)
if ap then screen.setColor(255,0,0) screen.drawText(w-10,10,"AP") end
--fuel flow local totalFuel = fuel * fuelMultiplier local endurance = totalFuel / fuelFlow local range = endurance/60 * speedKnots if fuelRateMode == 0 then -- endurance fuelRateValue, fuelRateExt = endurance, "min" elseif fuelRateMode == 1 then -- range fuelRateValue, fuelRateExt = range, " nm" else -- rate fuelRateValue, fuelRateExt = fuelFlow, "lpm" end screen.setColor(0,255,0) local fuelFlowText = math.min(math.max(math.floor(fuelRateValue+0.5),0),999) .. " " .. fuelRateExt screen.drawTextBox(3, 3, 40, 5, fuelFlowText, -1, 0) screen.drawRect(1, 1, 41, 8)
--battery display screen.setColor(255,255,0) batteryfill = math.floor(battery * 8) screen.drawRectF(17,31-batteryfill,4,batteryfill) screen.drawText(17,17,"b")
--fuel display screen.setColor(255,0,0) fuelFill = math.floor(totalFuel / fuelMax * 8) screen.drawRectF(11,31-fuelFill,4,fuelFill) screen.drawText(11,17,"F")
-- Fuel and Battery decorative boxes screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawRect(17,23,4,8) screen.drawRect(11,23,4,8)
-- gear display screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawTextBox(w/2-6,3,20,4,"G:" .. math.floor(currentGear), 0, 0)
-- sounding screen.drawTextBox(w-23,3,20,5,math.floor(sounding+0.5).."m", 1, 0) end
function drawTick(cx, cy, bearing, beginRadius, length) local b = math.rad(bearing) function f(r) return cx + r*math.sin(b), cy - r*math.cos(b) end local x0, y0 = f(beginRadius) local x1, y1 = f(beginRadius + length) screen.drawLine(x0, y0, x1, y1) end

wasActive = false isActive = false lastAPPush = false
function onTick() local valid = input.getBool(1) local apPush = input.getBool(2) if valid then if apPush and not lastAPPush then isActive = not isActive end local wp = {input.getNumber(2),input.getNumber(3)} local compass = input.getNumber(4)*-360 local gps = {input.getNumber(5),input.getNumber(6)} local turn = turnTo(wp, gps, compass) output.setNumber(1, turn) else output.setNumber(1, 0) isActive = false end output.setBool(1, isActive) output.setBool(2, not valid and wasActive) wasActive = isActive lastAPPush = apPush end
function turnTo(tgt, gps, heading) local h = clampBearing(heading) local t = clampBearing(math.atan(tgt[1]-gps[1],tgt[2]-gps[2])*180/math.pi) local pDist = t>h and t-h or (360-h)+t local nDist = t>h and (360-t)+h or h-t if nDist < pDist then return -nDist else return pDist end end
function clampBearing(b) return ((b%360)+360)%360 end

ticks = 0 activeTicks = 0 silentTicks = 0
function onTick() depth = input.getNumber(1) beginDepth = input.getNumber(2) continuousDepth = input.getNumber(3) beginTicks = math.floor(input.getNumber(4)*60) ticksToPlay = math.floor(input.getNumber(5)) if activeTicks == 0 and depth < beginDepth then local silence = math.max(lerp(depth, beginDepth, beginTicks, continuousDepth, 1), 1) if silentTicks >= silence then silentTicks = 0 activeTicks = ticksToPlay + 1 end end if activeTicks == 0 then silentTicks = silentTicks + 1 else activeTicks = activeTicks - 1 end output.setBool(1, activeTicks > 0) ticks = ticks + 1 end
function lerp(x,minX,minY,maxX,maxY) return minY+((x-minX)/(maxX-minX))*(maxY-minY) end

object.script:
zoom=2 zoomScale=1.05 wpShow=false currWP=1 inputWP=0 ticks=0 NUM_WP=8 wps={} buttons={} nextButton=1 function button(a,b,c,d,e,f,g,h,i,j) local k=function() return true end buttons[nextButton]={rect={a,b,c,d},text=e or"" ,debounce=f,press=g or k,en=h or k,draw=i or drawButton,preText=j or k,wasPressed=false,pressed=false} nextButton=nextButton+1 end
function drawSelector(l,m) if m==currWP then drawButton(l,true) end end
function drawInput(l,m) if m==inputWP and ticks//20%2==0 then l.text="" else if not wps[m].active then l.text="-------" else local n=wpDist(m)l.text=string.format("%.1fnm" ,n) end end drawButton(l) end
function moveWP(m,o) local p=m+o if p>=1 and p<=NUM_WP then local q=wps[p]wps[p]=wps[m]wps[m]=q end end
function removeWP(m) for r=m,NUM_WP-1 do wps[r]=wps[r+1]end wps[NUM_WP]={posn={0,0},active=false} end
function drawButton(l,s) if not l:en() then return end local t=screen col(50,50,50) if not s then if l.pressed then t.drawRectF(l.rect[1],l.rect[2],l.rect[3]-1,l.rect[4]-1) col(255,255,255)else t.drawRect(l.rect[1],l.rect[2],l.rect[3]-1,l.rect[4]-1) end end l:preText() t.drawText(l.rect[1]+2,l.rect[2]+2,l.text) end button(0,55,8,9,"-" ,false,function() zoom=zoom*zoomScale end) button(7,55,8,9,"+" ,false,function() zoom=zoom/zoomScale end) button(88,55,8,9,"w" ,true,function() wpShow=not wpShow end) for r=1,NUM_WP do local b=(r-1)*8 wps[r]={posn={0,0},active=false} local h=function() return wpShow end local u=function() if r==currWP then screen.setColor(255,255,0) end end button(14,b-1,8,9,">" ,true,function() currWP=r end,h,function(l) drawSelector(l,r)end,u) button(21,b-1,8,9,r,true,function() currWP=r end,h,nil,u) button(28,b-1,40,9,"" ,true,function() inputWP=r end,h,function(l) drawInput(l,r)end,u) button(67,b-1,8,9,"^" ,true,function() moveWP(r,-1)end,h,nil,u) button(74,b-1,8,9,"v" ,true,function() moveWP(r,1)end,h,nil,u) button(81,b-1,8,9,"x" ,true,function() removeWP(r)end,h,nil,u) end
function onTick() inputX=input.getNumber(3) inputY=input.getNumber(4) isPressed=input.getBool(1) gps={input.getNumber(6),input.getNumber(7)} keypad={input.getNumber(8),input.getNumber(9)} local v=input.getNumber(10) keypadPulse=input.getBool(2) for w,l in pairs(buttons)do l.pressed=l:en() and inputIn(l.rect[1]+1,l.rect[2]+1,l.rect[3]-2,l.rect[4]-2) if l.pressed then if not l.debounce or not l.wasPressed then l:press() end l.wasPressed=true else l.wasPressed=false end end if keypadPulse and inputWP~=0 then wps[inputWP].posn=keypad wps[inputWP].active=true if currWP>NUM_WP and inputWP==1 then currWP=1 end inputWP=0 end while currWP<=NUM_WP do if wpDist(currWP)<v or not wps[currWP].active then currWP=currWP+1 else break end end local x=1 for r=1,NUM_WP do output.setBool(r,false) end for r=currWP,NUM_WP do if wps[r].active then output.setBool(x,true) output.setNumber(x*2,wps[r].posn[1]) output.setNumber(x*2+1,wps[r].posn[2]) x=x+1 end end output.setNumber(1,zoom) output.setNumber(20,gps[1]) output.setNumber(21,gps[2]) ticks=ticks+1 end
function inputIn(a,b,c,d) return isPressed and inputX>a and inputY>b and inputX<a+c and inputY<b+d end
function onDraw() local t=screen if wpShow then col(0,0,0) t.drawRectF(14,0,74,64) col(50,50,50) t.drawRect(14,-1,74,64) end for w,l in pairs(buttons)do l:draw() end end
function col(y,z,l) screen.setColor(y,z,l) end
function wpDist(m) local A=wps[m].posn return math.sqrt((A[1]-gps[1])^2+(A[2]-gps[2])^2)/1852 end

lastBeep = nil lastObs = nil minObsDist = 100 ticks = 0 answer = nil distAcc = {0,0}
function onTick() local beep = input.getBool(1) local gps_x = input.getNumber(1) local gps_y = input.getNumber(2) if beep then if lastBeep then -- see: https://www.reddit.com/r/Stormworks/comments/jcaygi/comment/g9bo480/ local dist = 50.1 * (ticks - lastBeep) - 178 distAcc = {distAcc[1] + dist, distAcc[2] + 1} local d = distAcc[1]/distAcc[2] output.setNumber(3, d) local obs = {x=gps_x, y=gps_y, r=d} if not lastObs or vlen(vsub(lastObs, obs)) > minObsDist then answer = observe(obs) lastObs = obs distAcc = {0,0} end end lastBeep = ticks end output.setBool(1, answer ~= nil) if answer then output.setNumber(1, answer.bestGuess) output.setNumber(2, answer.altGuess) output.setNumber(3, answer.distance) end ticks = ticks + 1 if lastBeep and ticks - lastBeep > 2000 then -- about 100km, 33 seconds lastBeep = nil answer = nil observes = RingBuff:new() trilats = RingBuff:new() end end
RingBuff = { new = function(cls, sz) return { items={}, sz=sz, idx=0, write=cls.write, iter=cls.iter, } end, write = function(self, value) self.items[self.idx] = value self.idx = (self.idx + 1) % self.sz end, iter = function(self) local i = 0 return function() i = i + 1 return self.items[i-1] end end } observes = RingBuff:new(100) trilats = RingBuff:new(10000)
function observe(obs) for other in observes:iter() do local p0,p1 = trilaterate(other, obs) if p0 then trilats:write({ p0, p1 }) end end observes:write(obs) return makeGuess(obs) end
function trilaterate(p0, p1) local t = vsub(p1, p0) local d = vlen(t) if math.abs(d) < 0.000001 then return end local j = (p0.r*p0.r - p1.r*p1.r + d*d) / (2*d) local k2 = p0.r*p0.r - j*j if k2 < 0 then return end local k = math.sqrt(k2) local u = {x=t.x/d, y=t.y/d} local v = {x=u.y, y=-u.x} function posn(f) return vadd(vadd(p0, vmul(u, j)), vmul(v, k*f)) end return posn(1), posn(-1) end
function makeGuess(here) local sums = {0, 0} local errs = {0, 0} local n = 0 for tri in trilats:iter() do local b = { vbear(here, tri[1]), vbear(here, tri[2]) } if n == 0 then sums = b else local s = { sums[1]/n, sums[2]/n } local e11 = angdiff(b[1], s[1]) local e22 = angdiff(b[2], s[2]) local e12 = angdiff(b[1], s[2]) local e21 = angdiff(b[2], s[1]) if math.min(e11, e22) < math.min(e12, e21) then sums = { b[1] + sums[1], b[2] + sums[2] } errs = { errs[1] + e11, errs[2] + e22 } else sums = { b[2] + sums[1], b[1] + sums[2] } errs = { errs[1] + e21, errs[2] + e12 } end end n = n + 1 end if n == 0 then return end if errs[1] < errs[2] then return { bestGuess=sums[1]/n, altGuess=sums[2]/n, distance=here.r } else return { bestGuess=sums[2]/n, altGuess=sums[1]/n, distance=here.r } end end function vlen(v) return math.sqrt(v.x*v.x + v.y*v.y) end function vadd(a, b) return { x=a.x+b.x, y=a.y+b.y } end function vsub(a, b) return { x=a.x-b.x, y=a.y-b.y } end function vmul(v, f) return { x=v.x*f, y=v.y*f } end function vbear(from, to) local v = vsub(to, from) return (450 - (math.atan(v.y, v.x) * 180 / math.pi)) % 360 end function angdiff(a, b) return 180 - math.abs(180 - math.abs(a - b) % 360) end

radius = 20 tickLength = 3
function onTick() isActive = input.getBool(1) guessBearing = input.getNumber(1) altBearing = input.getNumber(2) distance = input.getNumber(3) heading = -input.getNumber(4)*360 end
function onDraw() local h = screen.getHeight() local cx = screen.getWidth()/2 local cy = h/2
screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawCircleF(cx, cy, 1)
screen.setColor(5, 5, 5) screen.drawCircle(cx, cy, radius)
screen.setColor(255, 0, 0) drawTick(cx, cy, heading, radius - 4, tickLength) if isActive then screen.setColor(5, 5, 5) drawTick(cx, cy, altBearing, radius + 1, tickLength) screen.setColor(255, 255, 0) drawTick(cx, cy, guessBearing, radius + 1, tickLength) screen.setColor(5, 5, 5) local nm = math.min(distance / 1852, 999.9) local text = string.format("%.1fnm", nm) screen.drawTextBox(cx - 20, h - 6, 40, 5, text, 0, 0) end end
function drawTick(cx, cy, bearing, beginRadius, length) local b = math.rad(bearing) function f(r) return cx + r*math.sin(b), cy - r*math.cos(b) end local x0, y0 = f(beginRadius) local x1, y1 = f(beginRadius + length) screen.drawLine(x0, y0, x1, y1) end

zoom=1 gps = nil waypoints = {} ticks = 0
function onTick() zoom = input.getNumber(1) gps = {input.getNumber(20), input.getNumber(21)} waypoints = {} for i = 0,7 do local active = input.getBool(i+1) if active then waypoints[i+1] = {input.getNumber(i*2+2), input.getNumber(i*2+3)} end end ticks = ticks + 1 end
function onDraw() local sc=screen local w,h = sc.getWidth(), sc.getHeight()
sc.drawMap(gps[1], gps[2], zoom)
local lx,ly = w/2,h/2 for _,wp in pairs(waypoints) do if wp then local px,py = map.mapToScreen(gps[1], gps[2], zoom, w, h, wp[1], wp[2]) sc.setColor(20,20,20) sc.drawLine(lx,ly,px,py) sc.setColor(0,0,255) sc.drawRectF(px,py,1,1) lx,ly = px,py end end if waypoints[1] then local dist = string.format("%.1fnm", distNM(gps, waypoints[1])) sc.setColor(5,5,5) sc.drawTextBox(15,57,73,7,dist,0,0) end end
function distNM(a,b) return math.sqrt((a[1]-b[1])^2+(a[2]-b[2])^2) / 1852 end
